to FERC Chairman Hoecker.  Due to technical difficulties, I could not attac=
h=20
the letter in a separate document, so I copied the letter and have reprinte=
d=20
it below.

Having never been involved in this type of letter writing campaign, this wa=
s=20
a bit of a stab in the dark for me, so I welcome everyone's comments.  I am=
=20
also working on a letter that could be sent by senior management or CEOs of=
